Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是…维甘的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.39,0:00:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是维甘的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎 来到维甘
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TXTA-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陌生的景象 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你不喜欢和敌人对话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 这里就是火星圈最大的卫星殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮二号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.36,0:03:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是那些被遗忘者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀着坚强的信念 建起的维甘的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了夺回地球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我力求建立最强大的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.65,0:03:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论技术 士气 军队向心力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无一不是顶级水准
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群被遗忘在火星的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何能拥有这样的军事力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经一切准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会负责收押俘虏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他暂时留在我这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的身份略显特殊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进展如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在分析
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在EXA-DB中搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对设计制造新型高达有帮助的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型高达？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人告诉您吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运用维甘的最新技术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设计制造新型高达
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是伊泽尔坎特大人的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达也是能凭空造出来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EXA-DB 实在超乎想象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那是旧国家战争时代的遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被禁止的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争本身虽然愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但讽刺的是 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科技却会因此迅猛发展
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说在那个时代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是一台最普通的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也远非现在可比
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而一位机师 则可以同时操纵几百台部件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至驾驶集战争技术于一身的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大规模杀伤性武器横行战场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们发现的还只是其中的极小一部分？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 正是这部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形成了维甘的现代技术基础
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦获得全部技术遗产会如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以实现的话 这场战争就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会宣告结束吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天佑我维甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被诅咒的秘宝 EXA-DB
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里就可以 退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你就是那位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在地球圈抓到的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这孩子难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的眼神对你没有任何好处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一声令下 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几秒钟后 你就会成为一具死尸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底打算带我来这里干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于张口说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会作为地球圈的代表见证这里的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见证维甘的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过今天旅途劳顿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经为你准备了房间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我负责照顾你 请叫我玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顾我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了 就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 所以才会被允许使用这间房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这张脸 简直像极了 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是伊泽尔坎特大人的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说好久以前就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.69,0:07:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪会给你特别待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则俘虏一般住不上这样的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.82,0:08:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 把身上的衣服脱下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换新衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要带我上哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我们为何要向地球联邦发动战争
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中的真正原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了侵略地球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵略地球？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是侵略 而是夺回
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们发誓不惜任何手段要重返地球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并夺回作为人的尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你们杀了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论有什么理由都不能这么做！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能够体会到吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被宣告「死刑」的人们的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「火星圈」「梦想中的新天地」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那不过都是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败的星球改造和磁力风暴所引发的不治之症
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使那里沦为一片死病蔓延之地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星圈的人们在与病魔的斗争中繁衍生息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,编织起了属于他们的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终有一天要重返地球家园！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这个心愿深埋心中 生存了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们选择战争
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为夺回这片名为地球的故土
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们战斗的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能够体会到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 就算这样 维甘也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:09:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ID卡和联络用终端
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以在城市中和我们取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者购买必需品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是你的目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必担心 过后会来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧 去了解一下维甘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去亲眼看看自己恨之入骨的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人真正的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.13,0:10:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有丑话说在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你时刻受到监视
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做无谓的尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过多少次了 不要再干这种事！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是这里的人吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TXTB-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.85,0:12:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没用 不过就是点擦伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我家 不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是小心点为好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近不太平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家活得都挺难的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被逼得走投无路了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去床上躺着！露乌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我叫吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我叫露乌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受伤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫狄恩 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～看起来不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.30,0:13:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧 一起吃顿饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和你聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露乌！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想听听外面的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么先告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧是从哪来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有点…远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在上学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的学校 教些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉欧擅长什么体育项目？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.74,0:14:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕吉欧 我也好想去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聊聊天 有时还吵嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一定很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没上过学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道 这种病需要卧床
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不治之症
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.10,0:14:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊泽尔坎特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个少年是高达的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不应该审讯他 从他嘴里收集情报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有到那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 时不我待啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.72,0:14:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有我的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说说吧 你们那边怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们那边？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是问你 你们卫星上的病情控制怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想说的话 那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经 活不长了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最多还有三个月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太不公平了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹她做错了什么非要死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的病 这么重吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以想想办法呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.30,0:15:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想办法？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便有药 也不可能照顾到我们这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不可能完全治好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是多活一段时间而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球上的家伙们在安全的地方享福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们却被迫过着这种生活
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太自私了 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:15:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊泽尔坎特大人总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会把我们带回地球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没有 看到妹妹那么开心过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好不要再来找我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的成了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对她来说 只有痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不可以来找我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己的身体 自己最清楚！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露乌！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…就算这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看看更多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看看更多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:17:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算去更多的地方 认识更多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离别马上就会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会徒增伤感…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得害怕迎接死亡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宁愿那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宁愿最后变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想活得像个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想活得像个人那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想和吉欧聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多事想问吉欧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.75,0:18:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲眼见证火星圈的现状后有何感想？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.95,0:18:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们总是为心爱的人着想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴望从家庭中获得温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在这里 如此单纯的愿望也会遭到践踏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘的人们因害怕失去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而刻意压制着感情生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 狄恩他们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.19,0:18:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你遇到的那个少年的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实大家小的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都保留有一份人类的感性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 随着长大成人 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便失去了那份爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不再执着于家人和恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕全心全意的去爱别人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们因为不愿被夺走情感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.51,0:18:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而发出的呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并非为死亡而悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是为不能活得像个正常人 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.33,0:18:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而伤心欲绝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真正的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是一场简单的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在之前的每一次战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都为你们提供了幸存的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对那些浑浑噩噩的地球种们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我始终都在向他们发问
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否有生存的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否有生存的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法理解！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊泽尔坎特大人对那位少年太缺乏戒心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是个孩子 毕竟是敌人的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得放松监视
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如有万一 由我们亲手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要那个少年的命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的 今天我又把那孩子错看成了罗米
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.69,0:20:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是命运的捉弄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诊断如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.89,0:20:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生说了 剩余时间不足六个月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须坚持
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要亲手打开通往伊甸的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 这是我们活到今天的目的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.74,0:20:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从失去罗米的那天开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离别马上就会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会变得害怕迎接死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宁愿那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宁愿最后变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想活得像个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想活得像个人那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗 吉欧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并非为死亡而悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是为不能活得像个正常人 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而伤心欲绝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们捕获高达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功阻止了联邦增强战斗力的企图
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸计划开始进入最终阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机来临了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.62,0:21:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为这一天赌上了全部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得吗 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次告诉你这项计划的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下从未有一天忘记过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.52,0:21:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为夺回作为人的尊严和权利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.13,0:21:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是这份崇高的志向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指引我战斗到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那就拜托了 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.07,0:21:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:22:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 伊泽尔坎特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.20,0:22:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 马上进入零部件的高速成型工序
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.75,0:22:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诞生自维甘的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的高达
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------NEXT-------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.88,0:24:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲的身影来到吉欧面前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.41,0:24:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在尝试脱逃的过程中
